---
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Learning Paths - Simon Gelbart" current="learning">
  <section class="page-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Learning paths</p>
    <h1>Practical learning material for backend and .NET developers.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Courses, lessons, exercises, samples, and talks organized around concrete engineering trade-offs.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="grid two-columns">
    <article class="card large-card">
      <p class="tag">In progress · C# · .NET</p>
      <h2><a href="https://simongelbart.github.io/dotnet-learning-lab/">Modern .NET Learning Lab</a></h2>
      <p>The learning lab remains published from its own repository so lessons, examples, and optional labs stay together.</p>
      <div class="actions card-actions">
        <a class="button" href="https://simongelbart.github.io/dotnet-learning-lab/learning-paths/modern-csharp-type-design/">Modern C# Type Design</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="https://github.com/SimonGelbart/dotnet-learning-lab">Repository</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
